item.title: CVE-2018-11757|2024-08-05T08:17:09.152Z -- apache%20software%20foundation -- docker%20skeleton%20runtime%20for%20apache%20openwhisk
item.description: In Docker Skeleton Runtime for Apache OpenWhisk, a Docker action inheriting the Docker tag openwhisk/dockerskeleton:1.3.0 (or earlier) may allow an attacker to replace the user function inside the container if the user code is vulnerable to code exploitation.
